        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3: Posterior portion of the body in dorsal view of Chaetostoma formosae sp. nov., holotype, ICNMHN 17114, adult male, 97.4 mm SL. The square detail shows the distal portion of the anal fin in posterior view; small arrows indicate the posterior dermal folds reaching the tip of the enlarged anal-fin ray in mature males.The large arrow indicates the distal portion of the anal fin for which the detail is provided. Scale bar in the square detail equals 3.3 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4901070/files/figure.png" .

